title: ELEMENT 'TRAVEL WELL' NICK GARCIA AND JULIAN DAVIDSON
description:
Nick Garcia and Julian Davidson cruise down to Element YMCA Camp to skate two new all-terrain vehicles shaped by the riders themselves. See these and the entire Element collection here:
http://elementskateboards.com

Music by:
Boom Chick
"Ghost of Bo Didley"
